<subSubSection id="1B966538E442FFF8FF1966C57E4BF887" pageId="44" pageNumber="45" type="materials_examined">
<paragraph id="533336B3E442FFF8FF1966C5798DF91B" blockId="44.[151,1436,1761,2038]" box="[151,928,1761,1786]" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">
<emphasis id="61F8EAA1E442FFF8FF1966C57BADF91B" bold="true" box="[151,384,1761,1786]" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">Material examined.</emphasis>
<typeStatus id="8C378811E442FFF8FE0966C67B92F91B" box="[391,447,1762,1786]" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">Type</typeStatus>
material, as in 
<bibRefCitation id="371D4B42E442FFF8FDE566C579B1F91B" author="Andersen, T. &amp; Saether, O. A." box="[619,924,1761,1786]" pageId="44" pageNumber="45" pagination="33 - 44" refId="ref50197" refString="Andersen, T. &amp; Saether, O. A. (1996) New species and records of Beardius Reiss et Sublette (Diptera: Chironomidae). Annales de Limnologie, 32, 33 - 44. http: // dx. doi. org / 10.1051 / limn / 1996003" type="journal article" year="1996">Andersen &amp; Saether (1996)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="533336B3E442FFF8FF4967217E4BF887" blockId="44.[151,1436,1761,2038]" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">
<emphasis id="61F8EAA1E442FFF8FF4967217BFFF8FF" bold="true" box="[199,466,1797,1822]" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">Diagnostic characters.</emphasis>
The species belongs in the 
<taxonomicName id="948C4D30E442FFF8FC8567227958F8FC" box="[779,885,1798,1821]" class="Insecta" family="Chironomidae" genus="Beardius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="44" pageNumber="45" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="truncatus">
<emphasis id="61F8EAA1E442FFF8FC8567227958F8FC" box="[779,885,1798,1821]" italics="true" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">truncatus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
group. The male can be separated from all other members of the genus by the combination of the following characters: median volsella absent; and inferior volsella strongly curved with tongue-shaped basal projection, not fused to the superior volsella.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="1B966538E442FFF8FF4967557830F833" pageId="44" pageNumber="45" type="description">
<paragraph id="533336B3E442FFF8FF4967557830F833" blockId="44.[151,1436,1761,2038]" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">
<emphasis id="61F8EAA1E442FFF8FF4967557B74F86B" bold="true" box="[199,345,1905,1930]" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">Description.</emphasis>
The male was described in detail by 
<bibRefCitation id="371D4B42E442FFF8FC8C67557E1AF86B" author="Andersen, T. &amp; Saether, O. A." box="[770,1079,1905,1930]" pageId="44" pageNumber="45" pagination="33 - 44" refId="ref50197" refString="Andersen, T. &amp; Saether, O. A. (1996) New species and records of Beardius Reiss et Sublette (Diptera: Chironomidae). Annales de Limnologie, 32, 33 - 44. http: // dx. doi. org / 10.1051 / limn / 1996003" type="journal article" year="1996">Andersen &amp; Saether (1996)</bibRefCitation>
. The structure considered to be the “median volsella” by 
<bibRefCitation id="371D4B42E442FFF8FE3D67B178CDF84F" author="Andersen, T. &amp; Saether, O. A." box="[435,736,1941,1966]" pageId="44" pageNumber="45" pagination="33 - 44" refId="ref50197" refString="Andersen, T. &amp; Saether, O. A. (1996) New species and records of Beardius Reiss et Sublette (Diptera: Chironomidae). Annales de Limnologie, 32, 33 - 44. http: // dx. doi. org / 10.1051 / limn / 1996003" type="journal article" year="1996">Andersen &amp; Saether (1996)</bibRefCitation>
must be regarded as a basal tongue-shaped lobe of the inferior volsella; median volsella is absent.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="1B966538E442FFF8FF4967F97E45F817" box="[199,1128,2013,2038]" pageId="44" pageNumber="45" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="533336B3E442FFF8FF4967F97E45F817" blockId="44.[151,1436,1761,2038]" box="[199,1128,2013,2038]" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">
<emphasis id="61F8EAA1E442FFF8FF4967F97B4DF817" bold="true" box="[199,352,2013,2038]" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">Distribution.</emphasis>
The species is recorded from 
<collectingCountry id="2B9B7623E442FFF8FD3F67F97906F817" box="[689,811,2013,2038]" name="Costa Rica" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">Costa Rica</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation id="371D4B42E442FFF8FCB467F97E71F817" author="Andersen, T. &amp; Saether, O. A." box="[826,1116,2013,2038]" pageId="44" pageNumber="45" pagination="33 - 44" refId="ref50197" refString="Andersen, T. &amp; Saether, O. A. (1996) New species and records of Beardius Reiss et Sublette (Diptera: Chironomidae). Annales de Limnologie, 32, 33 - 44. http: // dx. doi. org / 10.1051 / limn / 1996003" type="journal article" year="1996">Andersen &amp; Saether 1996</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
